ft\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-054-semver-compatible-modules\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 055: ORM\",\"description\":\"2022-04-27: First draft\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-055-orm\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 057: App Wiring\",\"description\":\"2022-05-04: Initial Draft 2022-08-19: Updates\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-057-app-wiring\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 058: Auto-Generated CLI\",\"description\":\"2022-05-04: Initial Draft\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-058-auto-generated-cli\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 059: Test Scopes\",\"description\":\"2022-08-02: Initial Draft 2023-03-02: Add precision for integration tests 2023-03-23: Add precision for E2E tests\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-059-test-scopes\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 60: ABCI 1.0 Integration (Phase I)\",\"description\":\"2022-08-10: Initial Draft (@alexanderbez, @tac0turtle) Nov 12, 2022: Update PrepareProposal and ProcessProposal semantics per the initial implementation PR (@alexanderbez)\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-060-abci-1.0\"},{\"title\":\"ADR ADR-061: Liquid Staking\",\"description\":\"2022-09-10: Initial Draft (@zmanian)\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-061-liquid-staking\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 062: Collections, a simplified storage layer for cosmos-sdk modules.\",\"description\":\"30/11/2022: PROPOSED\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-062-collections-state-layer\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 063: Core Module API\",\"description\":\"2022-08-18 First Draft 2022-12-08 First Draft 2023-01-24 Updates\",\"noindex\":true,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-063-core-module-api\"},{\"title\":\"ADR 64: ABCI 2.0 Integration (Phase II)\",\"noindex\":true,\"description\":null,\"href\":\"/sdk/next/build/architecture/adr-064-abci-2.0\"},{\"title\":\"ADR-065: Store V2\",\"description\":\"Feb 14, 202